The United States strongly condemns the ongoing attacks in Israel by Hamas terrorists from Gaza. President Biden spoke with Prime Minister Netanyahu and offered support to the Government and people of Israel. The United States asserts that terrorism is never justified and recognizes Israel's right to defend itself and its people. The US warns against any other party seeking advantage in this situation. The Biden Administration's support for Israel's security is unwavering. President Biden and his wife Jill expressed sympathy for the families affected by the violence and hope for a swift recovery for the wounded. The situation is being closely monitored, and President Biden will maintain close communication with Prime Minister Netanyahu.